                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Within the file:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;/mrlegacy/src/main/java/org/apache/mahout/cf/taste/impl/similarity/EuclideanDistanceSimilarity.java&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Mentions that the implementation should be sqrt&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/thumbs_down.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; / (1 + distance).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Once the equation is simplified, should be: &lt;br/&gt;
1 / ((1 + distance) / sqrt&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/thumbs_down.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Coded:&lt;br/&gt;
return 1.0 / ((1.0 + Math.sqrt(sumXYdiff2)) / Math.sqrt&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/thumbs_down.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But instead is (missing grouping brackets): &lt;br/&gt;
1 / (1 + distance / sqrt &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/thumbs_down.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Coded:&lt;br/&gt;
return 1.0 / (1.0 + Math.sqrt(sumXYdiff2) / Math.sqrt&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/thumbs_down.gif&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;);&lt;/p&gt;
